createBuildInfoFor

public static void createBuildInfoFor(java.util.List aList,
                                      java.lang.String aBuildNumberClassname,
                                      java.lang.String aDisplayName)
Creates a BuildInfo object and adds it to the list. The build number to use is gotten from supplied classname. The display name to use for the build info object is also passed in. This method fails silently without adding anything to the list if something goes wrong (typically a class not found exception).
